metadata.name: Flat Earth
metadata.description:
Imagine a world where gravity doesn't exist, where astronauts can float off into the abyss, where the sun and the moon are nothing more than celestial ornaments dangling above us. A world where you can fall off the edge of the Earth if you venture too far. 

But fear not, flat-Earthers, for there is hope yet. You can still prove your theory by simply setting sail on the seven seas and searching for the elusive edge of the Earth. Just be sure to pack a life raft and a compass, because you never know where you might end up...

Medium: AI + Photoshop  
Year: 2023
